01:07:30,733 --> 01:07:32,900
I don’t know how many thousand
in São Paulo, in Brasilia...

962
01:07:33,033 --> 01:07:34,667
[We got so close!]

963
01:07:35,006 --> 01:07:36,015
I think Brazil suffers
from premature ejaculation.

964
01:07:38,333 --> 01:07:41,100
